(KNOCK ON DOOR)

05:13.448 --> 05:15.515
I'm Agent Reynolds from the FBI.

05:15.525 --> 05:17.609
Mrs. Miglin?

05:17.619 --> 05:19.519
- What's happened?
- (GARBLED RADIO TRANSMISSION)

05:19.529 --> 05:22.222
- Can we come in?
- Is it that man?

05:22.232 --> 05:24.583
It would be better if we spoke inside.

05:24.593 --> 05:26.585
Are my children safe?

05:26.595 --> 05:28.561
Your children are fine, ma'am.

05:33.302 --> 05:35.260
REYNOLDS: <i>AT 8:50 this morning,</i>

05:35.270 --> 05:37.396
Gianni Versace, the fashion designer,

05:37.406 --> 05:40.432
was shot in Miami Beach.

05:40.442 --> 05:43.510
We believe the killer is Andrew Cunanan.

05:45.447 --> 05:48.415
The prime suspect
in your husband's murder.

05:54.556 --> 05:56.656
When will this end?

05:59.863 --> 06:01.608
Tell me.

06:02.331 --> 06:04.264
When will this end?

06:04.274 --> 06:07.530
We have over 300 agents
searching for him.

06:08.587 --> 06:11.204
How many more are going to die?

06:16.077 --> 06:20.088
How much more pain
do you think I can suffer?

06:22.857 --> 06:23.907
Two months.

06:25.219 --> 06:27.387
You had two months.

06:27.397 --> 06:29.389
You had his name, his photo.

06:29.399 --> 06:32.285
What did he have?
The money he stole from Lee?

06:33.191 --> 06:35.428
What has he been doing for two months?

06:36.515 --> 06:37.697
We don't know yet.

06:41.147 --> 06:42.897
What have you been doing?

06:43.605 --> 06:45.555
W-We've been looking for him.

06:46.341 --> 06:49.301
And where is he now? That man.

06:49.311 --> 06:50.917
I won't say his name.

06:50.927 --> 06:52.227
Where is he now?

06:54.583 --> 06:56.549
He evaded capture.

07:04.459 --> 07:08.575
Uh, Mrs. Miglin, we think it best,

07:09.044 --> 07:12.603
considering the proximity to the
murder, that you leave Florida.

07:13.268 --> 07:15.635
We have a flight standing by.

07:17.672 --> 07:19.496
I'm sorry.

07:19.965 --> 07:21.065
What flight?

07:22.131 --> 07:24.881
Cunanan might know
that you're filming here.

07:25.514 --> 07:28.481
You want me to run?

07:31.553 --> 07:35.388
You want me to hide from him?

07:38.360 --> 07:43.263
You provide whatever security
you think necessary.

07:47.369 --> 07:51.237
I have never missed a broadcast
in my life.

07:56.102 --> 07:58.545
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

08:04.486 --> 08:06.453
(CHATTER STOPS)

08:08.523 --> 08:10.457
(GARBLED RADIO TRANSMISSION)

08:11.660 --> 08:14.286
MARILYN: When I first started
in television,

08:14.296 --> 08:17.363
they gave me just 30 minutes
to make an impression.

08:17.373 --> 08:20.525
I only needed 20 minutes to sell out.

08:20.535 --> 08:24.471
Today, we are going to break
some more sales records.

08:26.508 --> 08:28.475
I am so sorry.

08:30.679 --> 08:33.313
I need it to stop.

08:36.384 --> 08:38.485
NEWSMAN (ON TV): <i>Police named</i>

08:38.495 --> 08:42.255
alleged serial killer Andrew
Cunanan as their only suspect

08:42.265 --> 08:44.357
in the execution-style murder

08:44.367 --> 08:47.595
of world-famous
fashion designer Gianni Versace.

08:48.463 --> 08:51.564
OFFICER: Cunanan is known
to be a male prostitute

08:51.574 --> 08:54.461
who services affluent clientele.

08:54.696 --> 08:58.171
Cunanan is well-educated, well-dressed

08:58.181 --> 09:00.240
and is very articulate.

09:00.250 --> 09:03.201
Cunanan should be considered
extremely dangerous

09:03.211 --> 09:05.237
and armed at this time.

09:05.247 --> 09:07.439
NEWSMAN:
Andrew Cunanan is already wanted

09:07.449 --> 09:09.508
in connection with four murders.

09:09.518 --> 09:12.418
He was recently added to
the FBI's Ten Most Wanted list.

09:12.428 --> 09:14.513
Police did not specify

09:14.523 --> 09:17.190
whether Versace knew his alleged killer.

09:18.527 --> 09:20.519
NEWSWOMAN: came as a shock to all.

09:20.529 --> 09:23.596
His wife, Marilyn Miglin, gave a
statement regarding the matter.

09:23.606 --> 09:26.299
MARILYN: What can you say about a man

09:26.309 --> 09:29.351
you loved passionately for 38 years,

09:30.372 --> 09:34.786
who exemplified courage and...

09:35.577 --> 09:37.757
honor and dignity?

09:38.446 --> 09:40.040
(CAMERAS CLICKING)

09:40.308 --> 09:43.216
We had a fairy-tale marriage.

09:45.764 --> 09:48.221
He was my prince.

09:50.559 --> 09:52.125
Thank you.

09:52.561 --> 09:54.527
- (REPORTERS CLAMORING ON TV)
- (TV CLICKS OFF)

09:59.334 --> 10:01.293
(BIRDS SQUAWKING)

10:01.303 --> 10:03.269
